data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET - BUYER FINANCING FELL THROUGH, NO FAULT OF SELLERS.  Fantastic opportunity for an investor, first time or savvy home buyer to own this roomy, traditional, two story home in a cul-de-sac in a quiet neighborhood, by giving it some TLC.  This home is on a basement with a partial brick water table on front exterior.  The front porch and two backyard patios offers great entertaining space with built in jacuzzi.  Full primary suite upstairs with walk in closet, along with two secondary rooms that have a roommate floor plan.  The basement has potential to turn into rental income as it provides a private ensuite (bedroom and full bath), separate laundry area, walk in closet, full kitchen with an open concept, and private, exterior entry with its own separate, concrete driveway.   This home is great for indoor entertaining too, as it has 2 separate dining areas (one with coffered ceilings).  There's a sunroom that gives plenty of natural light.  Private backyard and NO HOA.  Several flex and storage areas throughout.  Close by shops and restaurants. Don't miss out on its potential! New garage door and septic tank has been recently cleaned.
